# Logs Directory

This directory contains application logs for different environments.

Log files are automatically created based on the LOG_FILE configuration variable.

## Log Files

- `development.log` - Development environment logs
- `staging.log` - Staging environment logs
- `production.log` - Production environment logs

## Log Levels

- **debug** - Detailed debugging information (development)
- **info** - General informational messages (staging)
- **warn** - Warning messages
- **error** - Error messages (production)

## Note

Log files are not tracked in version control (.gitignore).
